<br>
And dang it Creepy, cut that out! You just made me reroll Griven, my Dark Elf Ranger! I dropped Light Armor and Alchemy, and picked up Mysticism and Enchantment. At level 1, I used a scroll to soultrap a rat, then used the charged gem to enchant a cheap amulet. It took two tries, but The Amulet of Band-Aids heals for 6-8 points 10 times before it needs to recharge. That's 60-80 points of healing... not bad considering I only have 45 HP's starting out. You've made a believer! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/ugharadin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gharadin</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_ball.gif" BORDER=0> at: 5/7/02 10:13:52 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/ucreepypete.showPublicProfile?language=EN>CreepyPete</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_lightning.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#5F9EA0>(5/7/02 10:12:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1108.topic&index=16>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Morrowind</span><hr size=1> I've restarted about 15 times so far, I think I finally got it with the char I posted. Keeping the Paladin guy, prolly, but may either add Alteration or Security to him. I HATE leaving a chest behind because it's locked. It chafes me. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT