The good: speed is 85!!! This guy flies. Int and agi both around 50something.<br>
<br>
The bad: kinda wimpy starting out. I have had to buy several damage scrolls to finish off people that were easy kills with my heavy armor/spear guy. No spells yet for each school of magic, the pet should help, I'd think.<br>
